data.description: Back on the market due to Buyers Financing falling through! This exceptional three-story townhouse in Brookfield on the Potomac presents a host of desirable features. It boasts a private patio, a fenced backyard, and a spacious deck off the kitchen leading down to the lower level. The kitchen comes fully equipped, complemented by two full and two half bathrooms, The townhouse spans over 2,400 square feet and includes a fully finished lower level perfect for entertainment. The main level features a gourmet kitchen with an island alongside a cozy living/family room. The upper level houses all bedrooms, including a large primary bedroom with an en-suite bathroom featuring a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Additionally, there is a sizeable rear deck ideal for enjoying morning coffee or evening chats. The community offers a riverfront park, picnic area, and river access. This beautiful townhouse includes a garage, 3 bedrooms, and 2.5 bathrooms. The first level has a versatile large room suitable for various activities like a media room, gym, office, or playroom. The second floor features an open-concept living space with a large living room and a spacious kitchen/dining area. The top floor boasts a stunning primary suite with a luxurious bathroom and ample closet space, along with two more bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a laundry area. Situated between Martinsburg and Hagerstown, making it ideal for commuters with its easy access to major routes like Route 11 and I-81 and I70. The community provides direct river access and is close to shops, restaurants, stores and more. Brookfield adds more value with its gated private recreation community with access to the Potomac River complete with an oversized boat ramp., playground, basketball court, and pavilion. This property is not only attractively priced but also spacious, offering various areas for relaxation or entertainment.  Sold as-is, the HOA includes river access, pavilion use, and common area maintenance. Schedule you’re viewing today to see all that this home has to offer!
